    <fr:title text="Sedonions">Sedonions</fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>definition</fr:taxon>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p>The <html:dfn>Sedonions</html:dfn> may be obtained by the Cayley-Dickson construction applied to the Octonions as a real algebra. It is a nonassociative algebra over <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {R}]]></fr:tex> (and may be considered as a nonassociative unital ring).</html:p>
  </fr:mainmatter>
